Properties.Caption: Просмотр месячных отчетов
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName] As [Группа], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_PERIOD].[CPERIOD] As [Период], Sum([REP].[SUMM01]) As [Графа 01], Sum([REP].[SUMM02]) As [Графа 02], Sum([REP].[SUMM03]) As [Графа 03] From (((((((((((((((((([REP] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID_PARENT]=[K_UL_PARENT].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Inner Join [K_LSR] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID1]=[K_LSR].[K_LSRID])) Inner Join [K_PR] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_PRID]=[K_PR].[K_PRID])) Inner Join [K_CS] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_CSID]=[K_CS].[K_CSID])) Inner Join [K_VR] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_VRID]=[K_VR].[K_VRID])) Inner Join [K_PS] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_PSID]=[K_PS].[K_PSID])) Inner Join [K_DEP] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_DEPID]=[K_DEP].[K_DEPID])) Inner Join [K_OT] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_OTID]=[K_OT].[K_OTID])) Inner Join [K_PKZ] With (NoLock) On ([K_LSR].[K_PKZID]=[K_PKZ].[K_PKZID])) Inner Join [K_PERIOD] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_PERIODID]=[K_PERIOD].[K_PERIODID])) Inner Join [K_TD_SUB] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_TD_SUBID]=[K_TD_SUB].[K_TD_SUBID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([K_TD_SUB].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB] In ('12','02') And [REP].[SUMM_TYPE]=0 And |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [K_TD].[CTD], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [DOC].[CDOC], [K_PERIOD].[CPERIOD] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр месячных отчетов
